{"tid":1988471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王喜！時代選中了你","createTime":"2020-04-25T08:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T08:42:32.000Z","uid":297241,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"281bb55c5be3ae54300d0f9b3419decec60f5739","tid":1988471,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:27:37.000Z","msg":"參選立法會 <br />\n邵仲衡：十畫未有一撇<br />\n<br />\n2020立法會換屆選舉9月舉行，昨日邵仲衡在社交平台上載他與王宗堯、黃毓民的三人合照，他們做出緊握拳頭的「加油」動作，並呼喚王喜，似有意參加選戰。<br />\n<br />\n邵仲衡寫道︰「9月出戰，撐唔撐先？有人話，香港人要我哋出嚟參選。<span style=\"color: red;\">呼叫王喜！時代選中了你。</span>」他在留言中標籤了黃毓民及王宗堯，未知他們是否有意參選9月立法會。記者聯絡邵仲衡求證？他回應說：「計劃中，十畫未有一撇！」"},{"pid":"1241ba450307f1dda02d45d31f34871ef269bc4d","tid":1988471,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:36:51.000Z","msg":"黃選功能組別 王選地區？"},{"pid":"818b13b3361d5f7a972afe0c0fdd31f1e57b42d7","tid":1988471,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1241ba450307f1dda02d45d31f34871ef269bc4d","tid":1988471,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:36:51.000Z","msg":"黃選功能組別 王選地區？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:37:36.000Z","msg":"屌 原來都係王<br />\n之前王宗堯好似話選功能組別 咁王喜地區？"},{"pid":"ed0d664a8022f6374c6bd5146d3da3602a603a91","tid":1988471,"uid":53844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"做多左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96afd8a7141703fd9b156a9552a4933855fb8bc4","tid":1988471,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"被選中既細佬"},{"pid":"7afa7fa14a9608b7c20b74a1042c658bb78af009","tid":1988471,"uid":186201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:42:32.000Z","msg":"我呼叫王喜 時代選中了你<br />\nWon't tremble when you try it<br />\nAll I know is I won't go speechless<br />\nSpeechless"}]}